{"tid":2338850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「聖誕取消了。謝謝你，中国。」","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T04:54:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":517,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2def3e46853df75bbf13f13bd49919e78cacee","tid":2338850,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201222/418045909432012800051672.jpeg/F9hjdEa4Sdkwd5ExQK_4LDGDMCkF9rQhjQvl0I0L5dA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201222%2F418045909432012800051672.jpeg%2FF9hjdEa4Sdkwd5ExQK_4LDGDMCkF9rQhjQvl0I0L5dA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=2f463ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為在英國發現了傳染性更強的新冠病毒新變種，當局進一步收緊防疫措施，英格蘭多區封城，原訂聖誕假期容許最多三個家庭聚會的「聖誕氣泡」亦要取消。<br />\n<br />\n當地時間12月20日，英國脫歐黨（Brexit Party）領袖法拉奇（Nigel Farage）在Twitter發文諷刺：「聖誕取消了。謝謝你，中國。」並將該推文置頂，引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒《中國日報》駐歐盟社長陳衛華當即在上述推文以英文回覆稱，「戴上口罩，別再胡說八道。」（Wear a mask and stop talking sh*t）<br />\n<br />\n法拉奇則指責陳衛華的回應「有侵略性」&mdash;&mdash;他轉發陳衛華給他的回覆並揚言「中國共產黨不喜歡真相，並經常做出有侵略性的回應。他們應當為製造這場全球災難，向西方賠款。」<br />\n<br />\n其後陳衛華回覆稱：「有侵略性？對待像你這樣的特朗普式的種族主義者，不能太客氣。」<br />\n<br />\n法拉奇這種指責中國的說辭，有網民應和道「謝謝你將矛頭指向了正確的方向，中國。」但也有網友駁斥稱，「中國沒有嘲笑英國；中國沒有完全錯誤理解英國的抗疫策略；中國沒有把資本的利益置於民眾生命之上；中國沒有搞砸病毒檢測與追蹤；中國沒有嘲笑封城。這些帳，要算到你輔佐的首相頭上。」<br />\n<br />\n在發現變異毒株後，為防止疫情反彈，英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）宣布提升倫敦等地疫情防控級別。依據新規，20日起的未來兩周內，提升倫敦及周邊地區防疫級別至新增的第4級；未來兩周，英國30%的人口再度面臨「封城」。同時，倫敦和英格蘭東南部地區實行宵禁，超過1,600萬英國人被要求待在家裏，政府也取消了在聖誕節放鬆社交規定的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01. com/即時中國/564738</code></pre>"},{"pid":"cdfe03a86bbe30d1ce3718658a0acdd15b4d7918","tid":2338850,"uid":371558,"like":39,"dislike":702,"score":-663,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4adea9463b8aac8ee981171eecb1c4b801a2a3e9","tid":2338850,"uid":184679,"like":236,"dislike":4,"score":232,"quote":{"pid":"cdfe03a86bbe30d1ce3718658a0acdd15b4d7918","tid":2338850,"uid":371558,"like":39,"dislike":702,"score":-663,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"肺炎前面好似少咗d字<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c1d342051b07107c0cbe246d715a340c9a6730","tid":2338850,"uid":90660,"like":79,"dislike":4,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎係支那搞出嚟㗎記住啦"},{"pid":"9bb8e3c67737cc5f88d24db9f854bd78cd2790e9","tid":2338850,"uid":25059,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"中國都冇聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652252acb8ded0f422e418c0f523addcbfb76d3b","tid":2338850,"uid":17641,"like":81,"dislike":4,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>英國人應該慶祝春節代替聖誕節</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7652caa47332d46ceaa05b289b3c18f4917edb60","tid":2338850,"uid":253016,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"屌你呢條友葉問黎<br />\n打哂班歐豬一打十<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7546d606253b3e8bb2c8658a7447198140ac82","tid":2338850,"uid":184679,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Thank you Chi na<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Stop talking Shit"},{"pid":"0b66e2abba7fed1c8b70687ec00c366eb182e137","tid":2338850,"uid":37596,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"英國唔滅支那既下場"},{"pid":"d6cec6c3d084426be9bf8c347d16131d848b8285","tid":2338850,"uid":185656,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"4adea9463b8aac8ee981171eecb1c4b801a2a3e9","tid":2338850,"uid